Dear Richard,

Thank you for registering with Europe's fastest-growing community
of business professionals interested in news and information
about the European Union. Please keep this message for future
reference as I am sure you will find it helpful in finding your
way around the service.

We aim to provide you with fast and easy access to the whole
range of EU legislation and policies which are likely to affect
business in your industry sector.

We also provide you with the facilities to link up with like-
minded businessmen and women, as well as EU information
professionals, consultants and experts to help you make the best
use of the information we provide.

EUbusiness main features
========================

EUbusiness Week
---------------
Our free weekly e-mail newswire keeps you fully up-to-date
with key EU developments, such as news, legislation,
contract opportunities, documents and events, likely to
affect your business. Brought direct to your desk by the
start of business every Friday.
http://www.eubusiness.com/pastnews/index.html

EMUbusiness
-----------
Our free twice-monthly newswire on EMU and the euro, edited by
Marion Bywater, keeps you informed on euro-area governments'
decisions in fields such as tax, accounting and introduction of
notes and coins. To receive this you will need to update your
EUbusiness membership profile at http://www.eubusiness.com/profile
and click on the My Services tab.

EUbusiness subscription service
-------------------------------
Our subscription service allows you to access:
- our up-to-the-minute newsfeed provided by AFP, the world's
oldest established news agency, with comprehensive coverage of
the key events in the EU, as well as early alerts as to what is
happening behind-the-scenes in Brussels.
http://www.eubusiness.com/afpnews/
- the EUbusiness archive of over 3,000 stories, including all our
stories over two weeks old.
http://www.eubusiness.com/restricted/restricted_archive.html

Inside the EU
----------
Our daily news from the European Union is categorised into
sectors where you can find news, background information and web
links directly relevant to your business and interests.

