Finance
-------
Visit the Finance Business Community for news and info on
the European Central bank, the euro, sources of EU finance,
as well as markets, stocks and shares and our currency
converter.
http://www.eubusiness.com/finance/

EU Countries
------------
Demographic, economic, trade and tax information for the EU and
EU candidate countries, as well as selected web links.
http://www.eubusiness.com/western_europe/index.html
http://www.eubusiness.com/eastern_europe/index.html

Tenders
-------
A daily selection of contract opportunities from the Official
Journal of the European Communities (OJS), supplied by Tenders
Electronic Daily.
http://www.eubusiness.com/tenders/

PressZONE
---------
Publish your own news and EU information articles directly onto
EUbusiness. PressZONE is an ideal way to promote your company's
services to EUbusiness' worldwide audience of over 17,000
consultants, national government and European Union officials,
and high level business people from around the world interested
in EU affairs.
http://www.eubusiness.com/presszone/

Jobs
---------
If you are looking for a new job, or are a recruitment agency or
direct employer looking for a cost-effective route to quality
candidates, check out our CareerZONE directory, which we hope
will become a comprehensive source of European Union-related
human resources and training vacancies on the Internet.
http://www.eubusiness.com/cgi-site/eubjobs.cgi

Consultants directory
---------
If you are a member of a consultancy or a law firm specialising
in EU affairs, your EUbusiness membership entitles you to a free
basic listing in our Consultants Directory. You can enhance your
listing for a very reasonable fee.
http://www.eubusiness.com/cgi-site/eubconsultants.cgi

EUbusiness Search Engine
------------------------
You can search our site for news and information, or search our
comprehensive directory of EU-related web links, indexed every
day so the results remain focused and up-to-date.
http://www.eubusiness.com/search/

Business forum
----------------
If you're looking for a business partner, buyer, agent, supplier,
or a new job - visit our business-to-business forum.
http://www.eubusiness.com/discussion/

Any Answers
-----------
Answer questions, or post your own, in our Any Answers section.
http://www.eubusiness.com/help/anyanswers/

Poll
